#=
A simple collider which follows the camera so that enemies can test to see if they're on the screen.
Offscreen enemies won't shoot.
Well. The spiders will still shoot their webs offscreen. I thought that might make things more interesting :)
=#

Start
    # leaving a buffer of 20px on each side.
    setcollider 440 320

    setattribute tag "active_zone"
End
